<h2>Composability</h2>

<p>
  When the button is clicked the box should fly
  on or off the screen.
</p>

<p>
  If an HTML element has the ".flyable" class it will be hidden
  off the screen.
</p>

<p>
  You can then add the ".flyable-open" class to animate the element
  back onto the screen when isOpen is true.
</p>

<button {{action "toggleIsOpen"}}>
  Toggle isOpen
</button>

<p>
  isOpen: {{isOpen}}
</p>

{{#x-flyable isOpen=isOpen}}
  {{x-square}}
{{/x-flyable}}

